. 3 Female 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Liphistiidae" genus="Heptathela" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Heptathela yanbaruensis" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yanbaruensis">Heptathela yanbaruensis</taxonomicName>
Haupt, 1983 (XUX-2014-038A) 4 Male 
